
@startuml timer-uml

actor User
participant TimerControlView
participant TimerController
participant CountdownTimer
participant IntervalTicker
participant IDisplay
participant ISoundPlayer

== ① タイマー設定 ==
User -> TimerControlView : 時間を選択
TimerControlView -> TimerController : 時間設定完了(seconds)
TimerController -> CountdownTimer : setTime(seconds)
TimerController -> IDisplay : updateTime(seconds)

== ② タイマー開始 ==
User -> TimerControlView : 開始ボタンを押す
TimerControlView -> TimerController : onStartClicked()

TimerController -> CountdownTimer : start()
CountdownTimer -> IntervalTicker : startRepeatingTick()

== ③ カウント中 ==
loop 1秒ごと
    IntervalTicker -> CountdownTimer : tick()
    CountdownTimer -> CountdownTimer : 残り時間を1秒減らす
    CountdownTimer -> CountdownTimer : onTick callbackを実行
    TimerController -> IDisplay : updateTime(remainingTime)
end

== ④ 時間到達（通知） ==
IntervalTicker -> CountdownTimer : tick()
CountdownTimer -> CountdownTimer : 残り時間を1秒減らす

alt 残り時間が0になった
    CountdownTimer -> IntervalTicker : stopTicking()
    CountdownTimer -> CountdownTimer : onFinished callbackを実行
    TimerController -> TimerController : onTimerFinished()
    TimerController -> ISoundPlayer : startSound()
    TimerController -> IDisplay : showTimerFinished("タイマーが終了しました")
    TimerController -> IDisplay : updateTime(0)
end

== ⑤ 停止 ==
User -> TimerControlView : 停止ボタンを押す
TimerControlView -> TimerController : onStopClicked()

TimerController -> CountdownTimer : stop()
TimerController -> ISoundPlayer : stopSound()
TimerController -> IDisplay : updateTime(0)

@enduml
